<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="105" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="16" pageNumber="105">Culture characteristics.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="16" pageNumber="105">On PDA, cultures are initially white, becoming fuscous black in the centre and edge after 5 d. The colonies are felty with an irregular edge; texture uniform; sterile.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
